requestBody.description: Contains properties of a Campaign Manager subaccount.

accountId.description: ID of the account that contains this subaccount. This is a read-only field that can be left blank.

availablePermissionIds.description: IDs of the available user role permissions for this subaccount.

id.description: ID of this subaccount. This is a read-only, auto-generated field.

kind.description: Identifies what kind of resource this is. Value: the fixed string "dfareporting#subaccount".

name.description: Name of this subaccount. This is a required field. Must be less than 128 characters long and be unique among subaccounts of the same account.
